OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FCouzens was given a whole-life jail
OL,8,Fterm at the end of his Old Bailey
OL,9,Ftrial in September 2021, and the
OL,10,Fpowerful victim impact statement made
OL,11,Fby Ms Everard's mother led to the
OL,12,Funmasking of another predator hiding
OL,13,Fin the ranks of the Met.
OL,15,FOne of the victims of David Carrick
OL,16,Fwas moved to come forward and make a
OL,17,Freport to the police, which eventually
OL,18,Fled to his conviction as a serial
OL,19,Frapist.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FThe cases led to two damning reviews `
OL,8,Fone a report by Baroness Louise Casey
OL,9,Fin March 2023 that found the Met was
OL,10,Finstitutionally racist, misogynist and
OL,11,Fhomophobic.
OL,13,FThen an inquiry by Dame Elish
OL,14,FAngiolini in February 2024 concluded
OL,15,Fthat the Met and two other police
OL,16,Fforces could and should have stopped
OL,17,FCouzens being a police officer.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
