PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FSir Mark spearheaded efforts to clean
OL,8,Fup the Met, with 1,500 officers and
OL,9,Fstaff having been sacked, resigned or
OL,10,Fretired in the past three years.
OL,12,FBut in September last year he warned
OL,13,F"toxic or corrupt networks or cliques"
OL,14,Fthat might be resistant to change
OL,15,Fremained in the force.
OL,17,FThis followed undercover reporting at
OL,18,FCharing Cross police station by
OL,19,FPanorama that led to accusations of
OL,20,Fexcessive use of force and offensive
OL,21,Fdiscriminatory comments.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
