OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FSir Mark went on: "This tragic case
OL,8,Falso brought into sharp focus the need
OL,9,Ffor a national reset in how policing,
OL,10,Fand society more widely, prioritises
OL,11,Ftackling violence against women and
OL,12,Fgirls, as starkly illustrated by the
OL,13,FAngiolini Review.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@SOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,F"With the painful reality that far too
OL,8,Fmany remain victimsurvivors and still
OL,9,Fdo not feel safe, this anniversary is
OL,10,Fmore than symbolic.
OL,12,F"It is a reminder of our duty to the
OL,13,Fmillions of women and girls who move
OL,14,Fthrough London every day with a right
OL,15,Fto feel protected, not fearful;
OL,16,Frespected, not dismissed; believed,
OL,17,Fnot doubted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,F"We know we have not always lived up
OL,8,Fto that responsibility and must
OL,9,Fcontinue to repair the damage
OL,10,Finflicted on the trust of women and
OL,11,Fgirls in policing.
OL,13,F"I don't just see this as an
OL,14,Foperational priority ` it is also a
OL,15,Fmoral one, and one I am fiercely
OL,16,Fcommitted to."
OL,18,FThe mayor of London, Sir Sadiq Khan,
OL,19,Fsaid there is "much more work to do"
OL,20,Fto ensure women and girls feel safe in
OL,21,Fthe capital.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@NO]{D@OOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,F"Sarah's murder by a serving police
OL,8,Fofficer shocked and horrified the
OL,9,Fentire country and rightly sparked an
OL,10,Foutcry about the national epidemic of
OL,11,Fviolence against women and girls," Sir
OL,12,FSadiq said.
OL,14,F"In London, we are targeting the worst
OL,15,Fperpetrators of violence against women
OL,16,Fand girls, doubling down on standards
OL,17,Fwithin the Met and working to tackle
OL,18,Ftoxic misogyny in our society.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,F"But we still have much more work to
OL,8,Fdo to ensure women and girls feel safe
OL,9,Fand are safe in our city ` wherever
OL,10,Fthey are, whatever time of day or
OL,11,Fnight. As Mayor, I am determined to do
OL,12,Feverything in my power to help end
OL,13,Fviolence against women and girls as we
OL,14,Fcontinue to build a safer London for
OL,15,Feveryone."
OL,17,FFarah Naz, the aunt of Zara Aleena,
OL,18,Ftold ITV News London Sarah Everard's
OL,19,Fanniversary is a day to grieve all
OL,20,Fwomen murdered at the hands of a man.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FShe said: "Five years on from Sarah
OL,8,FEverard's murder and my thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith her family and it must no doubt
OL,10,Fbe a really heavy day for them.
OL,12,F"I think the grief sits with all of
OL,13,Fus. Grief that a woman can be
OL,14,Fassaulted and murdered. It's a grief
OL,15,Ffor all of us.
OL,17,F"Today is a day for all of us to
OL,18,Fgrieve that two women in the UK are
OL,19,Fmurdered each week and grief that
OL,20,Fwomen in the UK do not feel safe.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
