PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1772565072
OL,3,C'Extraordinary dignity' of Sarah
OL,4,CEverard's family hailed five years
OL,5,Cafter death
OL,7,FJess Phillips, minister for
OL,8,Fsafeguarding and violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls, said: "Five years on
OL,10,Ffrom Sarah Everard's tragic murder, my
OL,11,Fthoughts today are with her family and
OL,12,Fall those who loved her.
OL,14,F"I will do everything I can to ensure
OL,15,Fwomen and girls can live free from
OL,16,Ffear and harm ` something Sarah was so
OL,17,Fcruelly denied."
OL,26,@qD@XOUvD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
